name: GopherThetaStyle
description:
This is a Lora merge I made, combining styles that I thought looked really good together.

Works best around 0.65-0.75 weight area. It can be a bit finnicky and doesn't always handle hands very well.

WalnutCreamBlend was used for all examples.

modelVersions.description: First version. Don't remember exact weights used to make the final merge.
